# Build output / caches
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage

# Local dev artifacts
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/*.log
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store

# Tests + tooling we never need at build time
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx

# Docker artifacts
**/Dockerfile
docker-compose*.yml
**/.dockerignore

# Docs (image is leaner without)
docs
README.md
*.md
!apps/api/prisma/migrations/**/README.md

# Editor / OS junk
.cursor
.claude
